_sText:
This map is based around a specific area in Toronto, Canada. It is a DE map with 24 spawn points. It may lag on some computers because of the size.

I did not make this map, it was posted on another site by K_K_io 
(The original author)

The screens were taken from www.cstrike-planet.com and I take no credit for them.

If K_K_io wishes me to take it off then I will. 

On another note, this is my first time submitting a map. If I have done something wrong or it needs to be removed, then please do so after telling me why.
